targets.rawSql:
SELECT 
  positive
from data
order by year desc,month  desc,day  desc 
LIMIT 1

SELECT 
  recovered
from data
order by year desc,month  desc,day  desc 
LIMIT 1

SELECT 
  deaths
from data
order by year desc,month  desc,day  desc 
LIMIT 1

SELECT 
  vaccinated
from data
order by year desc,month  desc,day  desc 
LIMIT 1

SELECT 
  active_cases
from data
order by year desc,month  desc,day  desc 
LIMIT 1

SELECT 
	(year || ' ' || month || ' ' || day)::DATE AS "time", 
	positive AS "Positive Cases"
FROM data
order by time

SELECT 
  CURRENT_TIMESTAMP AS "time",
  PINCODE::varchar AS "metric",
  COUNT(*) AS "value"
from centers
where
  (year || ' ' || month || ' ' || day)::DATE = CURRENT_DATE
group by PINCODE

SELECT 
	(year || ' ' || month || ' ' || day)::DATE AS "time", 
	vaccinated AS "Total Vaccinated"
FROM data
order by time

SELECT 
	(year || ' ' || month || ' ' || day)::DATE AS "time", 
	tests AS "Tests Conducted"
FROM data
order by time

SELECT 
	(year || ' ' || month || ' ' || day)::DATE AS "time", 
	deaths AS "Deaths"
FROM data
order by time

SELECT 
	(year || ' ' || month || ' ' || day)::DATE AS "time", 
	first_dose AS "First Dose"
FROM data
order by time

SELECT 
	(year || ' ' || month || ' ' || day)::DATE AS "time", 
	second_dose AS "Second Dose"
FROM data
order by time

SELECT 
	(year || ' ' || month || ' ' || day)::DATE AS "time", 
	recovered AS "Recoveries"
FROM data
order by time

SELECT 
	(year || ' ' || month || ' ' || day)::DATE AS "time", 
	COUNt(time)
FROM centers
GROUP BY time

SELECT 
	(year || ' ' || month || ' ' || day)::DATE AS "time", 
	active_cases AS "Active Cases"
FROM data

SELECT 
	(year || ' ' || month || ' ' || day)::DATE AS "time",
    COUNT(*) AS "Central Delhi"
FROM centers
WHERE district_name = 'Central Delhi'
GROUP BY time

SELECT 
	(year || ' ' || month || ' ' || day)::DATE AS "time",
    COUNT(*) AS "New Delhi"
FROM centers
WHERE district_name = 'New Delhi'
GROUP BY time

SELECT 
	(year || ' ' || month || ' ' || day)::DATE AS "time",
    COUNT(*) AS "West Delhi"
FROM centers
WHERE district_name = 'West Delhi'
GROUP BY time

SELECT 
	(year || ' ' || month || ' ' || day)::DATE AS "time",
    COUNT(*) AS "North Delhi"
FROM centers
WHERE district_name = 'North Delhi'
GROUP BY time

SELECT 
	(year || ' ' || month || ' ' || day)::DATE AS "time",
    COUNT(*) AS "South Delhi"
FROM centers
WHERE district_name = 'South Delhi'
GROUP BY time

SELECT 
	(year || ' ' || month || ' ' || day)::DATE AS "time",
    COUNT(*) AS "South East Delhi"
FROM centers
WHERE district_name = 'South East Delhi'
GROUP BY time

SELECT 
	(year || ' ' || month || ' ' || day)::DATE AS "time",
    COUNT(*) AS "East Delhi"
FROM centers

SELECT 
	(year || ' ' || month || ' ' || day)::DATE AS "time",
    COUNT(*) AS "	Shahdara"
FROM centers
WHERE district_name = '	Shahdara'

SELECT 
	(year || ' ' || month || ' ' || day)::DATE AS "time",
    COUNT(*) AS "North West Delhi"

SELECT 
	(year || ' ' || month || ' ' || day)::DATE AS "time",

SELECT 
	(year || ' ' || month || ' ' || day)::DATE AS "time", 
	cont_zones AS "Containment Zones"
FROM data
order by time

SELECT 
	(year || ' ' || month || ' ' || day)::DATE AS "time",
  COUNT(*) AS "COVAXIN"
FROM centers
WHERE vaccine = 'COVAXIN'
GROUP BY time

SELECT 
	(year || ' ' || month || ' ' || day)::DATE AS "time",
  COUNT(*) AS "COVISHIELD"
FROM centers
WHERE vaccine = 'COVISHIELD'
GROUP BY time

SELECT 
	(year || ' ' || month || ' ' || day)::DATE AS "time",
	COUNT(*) AS "18+"
FROM centers
WHERE min_age_limit = 18
GROUP BY time

SELECT 
	(year || ' ' || month || ' ' || day)::DATE AS "time",
	COUNT(*) AS "45+"
FROM centers
WHERE min_age_limit = 45
GROUP BY time

SELECT 
	(year || ' ' || month || ' ' || day)::DATE AS "time",
    COUNT(*) AS "FREE"
FROM centers
WHERE fee = 0
GROUP BY time

SELECT 
	(year || ' ' || month || ' ' || day)::DATE AS "time",
    COUNT(*) AS "PAID"
FROM centers
WHERE fee > 0
GROUP BY time
